'''Vallachira Madhavan''' (May 17, 1934 &ndash; October 20, 2013) was a [[Malayalam]] novelist and short story writer from [[Vallachira]] in [[Thrissur District]] of [[Kerala]] state of India.<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.dcbooks.com/novelist-vallachira-madhavan-passes-away.html |title = Novelist Vallachira Madhavan passes away |publisher = DCBooks |accessdate = 2013-10-21 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131226141053/http://www.dcbooks.com/novelist-vallachira-madhavan-passes-away.html |archivedate = 2013-12-26 |deadurl = yes |df = }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mathrubhumi.com/story.php?id=399934 |title=Novelist Vallachira Madhavan no more |publisher=Mathrubhumi |accessdate=2013-10-21}}</ref>
